DTSTAMP:20260307T070429Z
DTSTART:20260312T230000Z
DESCRIPTION:Hey everyone\, \n\nAre you looking for a fun way to unwind afte
	r a long day at work? Join us every Thursday evening from 4-9pm for our al
	l-night happy hour event! \n\nWe’ve got a great selection of refreshing dr
	inks and delicious snacks featuring fresh seasonal flavors that you won’t 
	want to miss. Whether you’re in the mood for a classic cocktail or somethi
	ng new and exciting\, we’ve got you covered. \n\nSo gather your friends an
	d come join us for a night of good drinks\, good food\, and good company. 
	We can’t wait to see you there! \n\nDon’t forget to book a reservation so 
	we can reserve a spot for you. See you on Thursday! \n\nRESY: https://resy
	.com/cities/bol/the-cottage-bothell\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events
	/#/details/all-night-happy-hour-at-the-cottage/14928599/2026-03-12T00\n\nF
